<section xml:id="sec-1-5-Adding_and_Subtracting_Fractions" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Adding and Subtracting Fractions</title>
    <p><em>Adding and Subtracting Fractions</em> covers the process to find a common denominator 
        in order to find the sum of two rational expressions. This lesson relies on a knowledge 
        of <xref ref="sec-1-2-Factoring" text="title"/> Polynomials 
        and <xref ref="sec-1-3-Reducing_Fractions" text="title"/>.</p>
        
